{"tid":1216920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本人聯署抵抗送中","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T11:25:31.000Z","uid":206168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"20d8c632bfb3adad89f00f65a92b2da36afe5016","tid":1216920,"uid":206168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:25:31.000Z","msg":"轉載自FB專頁loveliver<br />\n<br />\n雖然這幾天暫時不會作更新，不過想分享這個日本團體Youth Democracy Promotion Agency起的網上聯署<br />\n<br />\n這項聯署連同了47位日本不同地區的議員，一同希望外務大臣對香港政府提出的逃法引渡修訂案、及政府使用暴力鎮壓示威者一事作出回應<br />\n<br />\n而這47位議員當中便包括了大家都熟悉的沼津市議員小澤隆，小澤議員也在推特上呼籲網民響應這個網上便能做到的署名活動：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/llllnumazullll/status/1139107616070688768?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fllllnumazullll%2Fstatus%2F1139107616070688768%3Fs%3D21&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=0568c8e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fllllnumazullll%2Fstatus%2F1139107616070688768%3Fs%3D21&h=059f1d20\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/llllnumazullll/status/1139107616070688768?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 因為是日本方面發起代表日本人聲音的聯署，大家不是日本國民就不用簽署這個了，可轉發至認識的日本朋友或在推特轉推讓更多人看到，謝謝<br />\n<br />\n團體官方網站：<br />\n<a href=\"http://youth-democracy.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyouth-democracy.org%2F&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=9007af65\" target=\"_blank\">http://youth-democracy.org/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TQsJph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TQsJph.jpg&h=23269fe8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ay2uWKi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAy2uWKi.jpg&h=0ba53962&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n949chE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn949chE.jpg&h=6a0aa112&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}